    "basmil_image_text_ByYF7C": {
      "type": "basmil-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "content_mRcgWJ": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Become Medicinal Mad Honey Distributor Today!",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p>Medicinal Mad Honey  is a community-based business in the heart of Nepal, dedicated to providing high-quality medicinal mad honey. We work closely with local <a href=\"/pages/honey-hunter\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"honey hunter\">honey hunters</a> from the land of mad honey to ensure the best product at every step—from collection and extraction to packing and testing.</p><p>Becoming a <a href=\"/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/\">Medicinal Mad Honey </a>wholesale distributor means partnering with a brand known for quality, trust, and reliability. </p><p>For the past eight years, we’ve been dedicated to sustainability, partnering with over 80 communities and more than 2,100 honey hunters across regions like Lamjung, Gorkha, Rukum, and Solukhumbu. This community-driven approach ensures the authenticity and reliability of our mad honey every step of the way.</p><p>Our latest facility in Kathmandu, established in 2021, features one of Nepal's most advanced honey-packing setups. We ensure every batch meets the highest standards by subjecting it to two rounds of independent testing, including <a href=\"/pages/grayanotoxin\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"grayanotoxin\">grayanotoxin</a> levels. Each batch is also sent for additional certification. </p><p>With a global vision, we supply our premium mad honey to discerning customers worldwide, offering a product that stands for purity, sustainability, and exceptional quality.</p><p>Interested in becoming a distributor of this rare, powerful product? Get in touch with us today! Fill out the form here or email us at <a href=\"mailto:contact@medicinalmadhoney.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Contact Medicinal Mad Honey\">contact@medicinalmadhoney.com</a> for any inquiries. Let’s work together to bring the benefits of medicinal mad honey to more and more people around the world.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text_2": "",
            "button_link_2": ""
          }
        },
